         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2483, recto: (1) [Before] (2) my humble affair, I, (3) Frange, the sinner, write (4) greeting his beloved good brothers (5) Theodore and (6) Pher.  Be so kind, my lord (7) and brother Pher, and come to me forthwith.  (8) Farewell in the Lord, my beloved good brothers.  (9) The holy Trinity...</ab>
